After we got married,
he just...

742
00:46:31,049 --> 00:46:32,093
[SIGHS]

743
00:46:32,137 --> 00:46:35,749
Nothing was ever
good enough.

744
00:46:35,793 --> 00:46:37,838
I wasn't smart enough.

745
00:46:37,882 --> 00:46:39,448
Well, I hope you
didn't believe him,

746
00:46:39,492 --> 00:46:43,365
because you are
the most interesting,

747
00:46:43,409 --> 00:46:46,107
attractive,

748
00:46:46,151 --> 00:46:47,848
herb gardener
I ever met.

749
00:46:47,892 --> 00:46:49,458
[LAUGHING]

750
00:46:51,809 --> 00:46:53,419
Well, you're not
so bad yourself.

751
00:46:54,855 --> 00:46:57,031
No?No.

752
00:47:00,992 --> 00:47:02,297
