00:47:10,218 --> 00:47:13,395
Van, it's Ace.
It's Ace, right there.Where?

755
00:47:16,007 --> 00:47:17,573
You sure?Yes, I'm sure.

756
00:47:17,617 --> 00:47:19,401
His hair's
