757
00:47:19,445 --> 00:47:21,142
Wait, now, wait a minute.
You're sure?

758
00:47:21,186 --> 00:47:23,318
Yes, I'm sure!

759
00:47:23,362 --> 00:47:25,233
All right, come on.
Let's go.

760
00:47:25,277 --> 00:47:28,193
