761
00:47:28,236 --> 00:47:30,282
Excuse me!
We've been waiting
almost an hour.

762
00:47:30,325 --> 00:47:32,066
Why do we even
need them?

763
00:47:32,110 --> 00:47:34,199
Calm down.
It's called due process.

764
00:47:34,242 --> 00:47:35,591
Let's just go.BECK: Sorry.

765
00:47:35,635 --> 00:47:38,159
