pileup on the highway.

766
00:47:38,203 --> 00:47:40,161
Is this about
the other night?

767
00:47:40,205 --> 00:47:43,077
As I told you,
Ms. Pritcher's ex-husband
kidnapped their son.

768
00:47:43,121 --> 00:47:45,471
Now, this is
a Superior Court order

769
00:47:45,514 --> 00:47:48,213
