we couldn't get a trace.

774
00:47:59,659 --> 00:48:01,966
If we screw this up,
and he gets away again,

775
00:48:02,009 --> 00:48:03,793
we're not gonna get
another chance.

776
00:48:07,145 --> 00:48:08,494
