00:49:07,814 --> 00:49:09,250
Police! Open up!

792
00:49:09,294 --> 00:49:10,643
Can't you just
break the door down?

793
00:49:10,686 --> 00:49:12,558
Open up!I know they're in there.

794
00:49:12,601 --> 00:49:13,689
Excuse me.

795
00:49:13,733 --> 00:49:15,909
Open up, bastard!
[GRUNTS]

796
00:49:17,345 --> 00:49:20,479
Ace? Ace?

797
00:49:25,701 --> 00:49:26,702
Ace?

798
00:49:26,746 --> 00:49:27,747
Ace!

799
00:49:38,062 --> 00:49:40,978
Look!
They're on a raft!

800
00:49:41,021 --> 00:49:43,806
Call the Sheriff!
Tell him we need
a helicopter or something!

801
00:49:43,850 --> 00:49:45,808
We don't have one.
State does, but it'd take
hours to get here.

802
00:49:45,852 --> 00:49:47,375
Uh, do you have a boat?

803
00:49:47,419 --> 00:49:48,811
Solomon!

804
00:49:48,855 --> 00:49:51,336
Tell Beck
they're on the river.

805
00:49:56,994 --> 00:49:59,126
LAEL: How far
does the river go?

806
00:49:59,170 --> 00:50:01,128
Three and a half miles

807
00:50:01,172 --> 00:50:03,261
to the Columbia.

808
00:50:06,655 --> 00:50:09,223
Do you think
we can catch them?

809
00:50:09,267 --> 00:50:13,662
I can't say. They may
have put to the shore
and gone up the highway.

810
00:50:13,706 --> 00:50:16,578
Well, if they didn't,
do you think we can?

811
00:50:16,622 --> 00:50:19,103
Well, they don't
know the currents,

812
00:50:19,146 --> 00:50:20,539
