813
00:50:20,582 --> 00:50:22,541
Maybe we can.

814
00:50:30,331 --> 00:50:32,464
Is that them?

815
00:50:36,468 --> 00:50:37,947
No.

816
00:50:47,392 --> 00:50:49,133
SOLOMON: Hold on.

817
00:50:57,054 --> 00:50:59,056
There they are
at 10 o'clock!

818
00:51:00,187 --> 00:51:01,884
SOLOMON: Oh, no!

819
00:51:01,928 --> 00:51:03,930
Tell them they're taking
the wrong fork.

820
00:51:03,973 --> 00:51:07,064
Mike! Mike!
You're going
the wrong way!

821
00:51:09,675 --> 00:51:10,937
What's over there?

822
00:51:10,980 --> 00:51:13,070
Some pretty bad rapids.

823
00:51:22,862 --> 00:51:24,777
VAN: Mike!

824
00:51:24,820 --> 00:51:26,605
Mike!

825
00:51:42,186 --> 00:51:44,144
VAN: That them?LAEL: Oh, my God!

826
00:51:44,188 --> 00:51:46,103
SOLOMON: I think so.

827
00:51:59,159 --> 00:52:01,944
No. Ace!

828
00:52:05,252 --> 00:52:07,124
Lael!
What are you doing?

829
00:52:10,562 --> 00:52:11,519
Lael!

830
00:52:22,400 --> 00:52:23,966
Help.

