834
00:52:37,328 --> 00:52:38,981
She's just across the hall.Okay, thanks.

835
00:52:39,025 --> 00:52:40,157
WOMAN ON PA:
Doctor Lawrence
with Pediatrics.

836
00:52:40,200 --> 00:52:41,984
Doctor Lawrence.

837
00:52:51,603 --> 00:52:54,649
The owner of a blue sedan
parked near
the Admitting entrance.

