839
00:52:58,044 --> 00:52:59,176
[SIGHS]

840
00:52:59,219 --> 00:53:00,612
[GROANS]

841
00:53:00,655 --> 00:53:02,962
Van,

842
00:53:03,005 --> 00:53:04,137
where's Ace?

843
00:53:05,617 --> 00:53:07,401
Um...

844
00:53:07,445 --> 00:53:08,663
They never found him.

845
00:53:08,707 --> 00:53:10,143
But that was their boat?

846
00:53:10,187 --> 00:53:11,710
Yeah.

847
00:53:27,508 --> 00:53:29,684
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

848
00:53:29,728 --> 00:53:30,772
Excuse me.

849
00:53:30,816 --> 00:53:34,428
Um, this isn't
a very good time.

850
00:53:34,472 --> 00:53:36,822
Well, maybe better
than you think.

851
00:53:36,865 --> 00:53:39,085
The police been
dragging the river,

852
00:53:39,128 --> 00:53:41,522
and they came up
with nothing, but...

853
00:53:41,566 --> 00:53:43,263
they did find
a set of tracks.

854
00:53:43,307 --> 00:53:45,526
Right downstream
from the raft.

855
00:53:45,570 --> 00:53:47,789
It was a single set,
a man's.

856
00:53:47,833 --> 00:53:49,922
Well, he could've
been carrying the boy.

857
00:54:03,283 --> 00:54:04,850
We are back.
I'm Sally Jenkins,

858
00:54:04,893 --> 00:54:07,156
