Oregon, but they disappeared.

863
00:54:17,210 --> 00:54:18,907
Since then she's had
no new leads.

864
00:54:20,996 --> 00:54:22,955
Alright, caller,
you're on the air.

865
00:54:22,998 --> 00:54:25,871
Hello, Lael?
Yes, hi.

866
00:54:25,914 --> 00:54:28,265
I don't understand
how your husband
could just disappear.

867
00:54:28,308 --> 00:54:29,570
I mean,
he has to work,

868
00:54:29,614 --> 00:54:31,442
and your son's
in school somewhere.

869
00:54:31,485 --> 00:54:33,879
Can't you trace them
that way?

870
00:54:33,922 --> 00:54:37,230
We've tried everything,
but nothing's turned up.

871
00:54:37,274 --> 00:54:39,363
The reason
I'm here today
is because...

872
00:54:39,406 --> 00:54:41,278
Well, I think
the only way
I'm gonna find him

873
00:54:41,321 --> 00:54:43,889
is if someone
who's seen him
calls me.

874
00:54:43,932 --> 00:54:47,240
What would you
say to that person
to get them to call?

875
00:54:50,330 --> 00:54:52,463
If you know
where my son is,

876
00:54:52,506 --> 00:54:54,465
please help me.

877
00:54:54,508 --> 00:54:56,031
He's only seven years old,

878
00:54:56,075 --> 00:54:58,643
and he has
severe asthma.

879
00:54:58,686 --> 00:55:01,385
He's supposed to
have shots to control it,

880
00:55:01,428 --> 00:55:02,995
but I don't think
he's getting them.

881
00:55:05,345 --> 00:55:08,087
I don't know how long
he'll make it without them.

882
00:55:10,350 --> 00:55:12,396
He needs to be home
so I can take care
of him.

883
00:55:14,746 --> 00:55:17,009
I'm sure he wonders
where I am.

884
00:55:17,052 --> 00:55:19,359
I didn't even
get a chance
to say goodbye.

885
00:55:23,058 --> 00:55:25,713
As much as
he needs me,

886
00:55:25,757 --> 00:55:28,281
the truth is I don't know
what to do without him.

887
00:55:46,517 --> 00:55:48,040
I heard you
on the radio.

888
00:55:49,650 --> 00:55:51,391
It's over between
me and Mike.

889
00:55:51,435 --> 00:55:55,439
He, uh, got a message
to me through Catherine.

890
00:55:55,482 --> 00:55:56,875
I guess I served
my purpose.

891
00:55:59,007 --> 00:56:00,705
Anyway, um,

892
00:56:00,748 --> 00:56:02,533
for what it's worth,
Catherine quit.

893
00:56:02,576 --> 00:56:05,100
She's, um,
going on a trip

894
00:56:05,144 --> 00:56:06,841
but she won't
say where.

895
00:56:06,885 --> 00:56:10,497
We're, um, we're giving her
a party tonight at the inn.

896
00:56:10,541 --> 00:56:12,151
I don't know
if this helps,

897
00:56:12,194 --> 00:56:14,109
but I thought
you should know.

898
00:56:20,333 --> 00:56:22,422
JOHNSON:
Unless you can show
probable cause,

899
00:56:22,466 --> 00:56:24,337
a judge won't issue
a search warrant.

900
00:56:24,381 --> 00:56:25,730
Now, we investigated her,

901
00:56:25,773 --> 00:56:27,427
she came out clean.
I'm sorry.

902
00:56:27,471 --> 00:56:29,386
But after tonight,
she's gone.

903
00:56:29,429 --> 00:56:30,691
I'm sorry.

904
00:56:35,348 --> 00:56:36,567
[SIGHS]

905
00:57:11,819 --> 00:57:13,604
