of the house covered.

908
00:58:08,267 --> 00:58:10,008
Halt!

909
00:58:10,051 --> 00:58:11,575
Mrs. Pritcher.

910
00:58:13,011 --> 00:58:14,578
Mrs. Pritcher!

911
00:58:18,712 --> 00:58:19,974
[PANTING]

912
00:58:29,418 --> 00:58:32,073
The police are
looking for me.

913
00:58:32,117 --> 00:58:33,727
I just broke into
Catherine's house.

914
00:58:33,771 --> 00:58:35,903
Look, I found out
she's leaving tomorrow,

915
00:58:35,947 --> 00:58:37,862
and I know she's on
her way to see Mike,

916
00:58:37,905 --> 00:58:40,125
so I thought I might find
an airline ticket or something

917
00:58:40,168 --> 00:58:41,343
But look, I found these
pictures of Ace.

918
00:58:41,387 --> 00:58:43,781
Are you out
of your mind?

919
00:58:43,824 --> 00:58:45,696
Why didn't
you call me?

920
00:58:45,739 --> 00:58:47,828
Because I didn't
want to ask you to
break the law with me.

921
00:58:47,872 --> 00:58:49,264
Lael, we're gonna
find Ace,

922
00:58:49,308 --> 00:58:51,528
but we can't do it
with you in jail.

923
00:58:51,571 --> 00:58:53,834
[SIGHING] Oh, look...

924
00:58:53,878 --> 00:58:55,967
Let me look at those.

925
00:58:58,926 --> 00:59:01,755
Oh. That RV has
an Arizona plate.

926
00:59:01,799 --> 00:59:04,410
