933
00:59:16,770 --> 00:59:18,555
Okay. Now...

934
00:59:18,598 --> 00:59:20,165
We'll just figure
all this out tomorrow,

935
00:59:20,208 --> 00:59:22,515
including what
we're gonna
tell the police.

936
00:59:22,559 --> 00:59:24,952
If we're lucky,
maybe Catherine
won't press charges.

937
00:59:24,996 --> 00:59:27,433
In the meantime,
I don't think
you can go home.

938
00:59:27,476 --> 00:59:30,915
Might as well just
stay here, okay?
Come on.

939
00:59:30,958 --> 00:59:33,308
LAEL: Hi.
Hi, Lael.

940
00:59:33,352 --> 00:59:35,310
VAN: Just keep working.
