01:03:00,646 --> 01:03:01,690
Yes, it is.

971
01:03:01,734 --> 01:03:03,910
Was your RV
recently in Mexico?

972
01:03:03,954 --> 01:03:06,870
Yes. Are you from
the insurance company?

973
01:03:06,913 --> 01:03:08,654
Where in Mexico?

974
01:03:08,697 --> 01:03:11,788
Near our summer home.
Who is this?

975
01:03:11,831 --> 01:03:13,615
It's a long story,
Mrs. Holling.

976
01:03:13,659 --> 01:03:16,531
